# Number of lines of code in TeX: 6
sub TeX {
  my $self = shift;
  return $self->SUPER::TeX(@_) unless $self->{params}[0]->type eq 'Matrix';
  my $M = bless {%{$self->{params}[0]}, open => '|', close => '|'}, ref($self->{params}[0]);
  return '\det'.$M->TeX;
}
